name: Still Life 3.0
description: Fizz Pop (b.1974), Still Life 3.0, 2010, 4200 x 3360 pixels:    Still Life 3.0 is a digital interpretation of Coenraat Roepel's, Still Life with Flowers, 1721, oil on canvas, 66.5cm x 52.5 cm; continuing to find inspiration in these magnificent Golden Age master pieces.  At the centre of one of the flowers can be found an imagined planet, as the project begins to play with scale within the digital medium.
